189
00:35:51,123 --> 00:36:07,218
subjectum apostolicae sedi firmitate privilegii consistit inconcusse dotatum permaneat locis et rebus, tam eis quas moderno tempore tenet vel possidet, quam quas futuris temporibus in jura ipsius venerabilis monasterii divina pietas augere voluerit ex donis et oblationibus decimisque fidelium absque

190
00:36:07,218 --> 00:36:10,490
ullius personae contradictione firmitate perpetua perfruatur.

191
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:29,399
